Because you unmercifully exert all your
powers
against us, returned the priest, when one
half of them would be as much as we could have
any reasonable chance of resisting. But, apropos,
I think we had better have this ceremony
performed
before dinner, and then we shall be at ease,
and have nothing to do afterwards but enjoy
