Maria, hear me, my love! said he; I have
never yet been insensible to the delight that arises
from worshipping God, and I hope I never shall.
But to obey thy injunction is in itself a pleasure,
distinct and rapturous, which until my heart
ceases
to beat it shall keenly feel; and even the first
of my duties, the worshipping of my God, shall
derive additional pleasure from thy commanding
it. Oh Maria! do not think me profane when I
say that religion appears to me more lovely when
it is recommended by thee.
They now heard the steps of Tonnaleuka
advancing
.
My children, said he, as he entered, you
are now about to separate. Let it be with
fortitude
and resignation. The will of heaven
respecing
you cannot be yet known. But repose
confidence
in your Great Father, and serve him; and
whatsoever accidents may befall you, be assured
